LifeHelpr.com is your personal space to keep organized. You will find a number of tools here to help you get things done and this page should give you a good overview of what each one does, how to use it, and why we do it that way.
<br/><br/>
<h1>User Dashboard</h1>
The user dashboard is your home for everything LifeHelpr. We have made it a one stop glance in to your LifeHelpr organized world.
<br/><br/>
You will notice that you have your "Top 5 Todos" that are undone, you have all of your lists to view, and you can see your categories with their stats. You can also add to anything with the convenient "new" links.
