<h1>Lists</h1>
A list (sometimes called a Simple List) is a collection of things you need. More info can be found <a href="http://lifehelpr.wordpress.com/2010/10/29/todos-vs-lists/" target="blank">here</a>. You can create as many of these "Simple Lists" as you need or want.
